                            <comment id="21035" author="johann" created="Mon, 10 Oct 2011 09:46:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Any news or shall we just close this bug? Please advise.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18049" author="johann" created="Thu, 21 Jul 2011 11:24:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure, lfs quota -uv $username /path should return those info.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
